Trying to quell a furious reaction from employees outraged that he stood to =
profit from a merger with Dynegy Inc., Kenneth L. Lay, the chairman and chie=
f executive of the Enron Corporation, decided late yesterday to give up a se=
verance package worth more than $60 million.=20
